What you need to know:

Economically, jobs were lost and environmentally, there was a lot of agricultural waste arising from unpurchased food.An April 2020 global energy review report indicated that countries with full lockdown were experiencing 25 per cent decline in energy demand per week while those with partial lockdown had 18 per cent reduction.Farmers and other agribusiness owners spend days and at times weeks in conferences, shows and trade fairs.Hygiene enhances biosecurity that is a good control measure for diseases that are transmitted through close contact such as mastitis.